Shaji Kumar, Yi Lin, Tom Martin - Relapsed Myeloma including bispecifics and CART. #ASH22

@DrTJM_MD We have done RCTs of Obs vs Len and Len/Dex. And obs vs Dara (results not available). 

The hypothesis is triplet will be superior. That’s why RCTs are going on. Rd vs DRd; and Rd vs IsaRd. 

We don’t recommend treating HR SMM indefinitely. It’s 2 years and stop.

